## Quick start

```bash
pnpm install                  # install frontend deps
pnpm tauri dev                # hot-reload native window
pnpm test                     # vitest --coverage (frontend track, 80% floor)
make test-rust                # cargo test + llvm-cov 75% floor (Rust track)
pnpm tauri build              # release build for the current OS
```

