## CLI / IPC contract (desktop-tauri role)

| Rule | Implementation |
| --- | --- |
| `bundle.identifier` reverse-DNS unique | `{{ identifier }}` |
| Strict CSP, no `unsafe-eval` | `app.security.csp` in `tauri.conf.json` |
| Capability grants per command | `src-tauri/capabilities/default.json` |
| All IPC via `#[tauri::command]` | `src-tauri/src/commands.rs` |
| Logs в†’ stderr, data в†’ IPC return | `tracing-subscriber` on stderr |
| Updater pubkey embedded | `bundle.updater.pubkey` in `tauri.conf.json` |
| Two-ecosystem license scan | `make audit && make deny` (cargo) + `pnpm audit` (npm) |

